<a title="To get to the vessels and/or the DECK House dockside facility"><strong>To get to the vessels and/or the DECK House dockside facility:</strong></a>
Turn left on Nagoya Way into Ports oâ€™ Call Village and go to Berth 78. The sign for it is yellow and black, but itâ€™s a bit difficult to find.Â  Look instead for the San Pedro Fish Market.Â  Our dock is to the right of the Fish Market, and is visible across an open grass area.Â  Park near the grass area (itâ€™s free!) and take the sidewalk at the right side of the grass near the Candy Shop.Â  The sidewalk dead ends, then turns right.Â  Just beyond the turn, youâ€™ll find the gate to our dock on your left. DECK House is the second shop (#P-3) on your right.

&nbsp;

<a title="To get to the office (Berth 73, Suite 2)"><strong>To get to the office (Berth 73, Suite 2):</strong></a>
Stay on Sampson Way past two stop signs â€“ Nagoya Way and Skytower Way.Â  At the third stop sign, youâ€™ll see an off-white, two-story building with a green stripe and signs for Utroâ€™s restaurant.Â  Turn left at that stop sign and follow the road around till you can turn right into the small parking lot by the restaurant.Â  Our office is in the top story of the building.Â  The door is past the front of the restaurant.

